@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dyzrea(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v1 + 0.90) * (v1 + 0.50 + v0 + 0.26)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.94 - v1 + 0.43)) / 0.66)
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.93) * tmp))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin(0.72))
    tmp = v0
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v0 + 0.98) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.61)))
    data[tid] = v0
